<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link729312" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=729312&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F1352558-does-the-book-cover-elizabeth-holmes%2Fanswers%2F729312-not-really-holmes-did">flag</a>
</div>
