<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1372648-why-does-the-book-s-title-not-mention">Why does the book&#39;s title not mention Theranos by name? Surely it would have sold more copies that way.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1372648'><a id="like_count_community_question_1372648" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1372648?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">9 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F37976541-bad-blood">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1372648-why-does-the-book-s-title-not-mention">3 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1372648-why-does-the-book-s-title-not-mention">See all 4 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

