<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer5720640267347388852">John Carreyrou is a Pulitzer Prize-winning reporter and a nonfiction author. His first book, <i>Bad Blood: Secrets and Lies in a Silicon Valley Startup</i>, chronicles Silicon Valley&apos;s biggest fraud.<br/><br/></span>
  <span id="freeText5720640267347388852" style="display:none">John Carreyrou is a Pulitzer Prize-winning reporter and a nonfiction author. His first book, <i>Bad Blood: Secrets and Lies in a Silicon Valley Startup</i>, chronicles Silicon Valley's biggest fraud.<br /><br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="5720640267347388852" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

